{"type":null,"faqId":33545,"title":"为什么手机在使用的时候会感觉到发热？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>智能手机发热是普遍现象，所有智能手机在电池耗电的时候都会发热。同时，Android手机允许多后台应用任务并发执行，保证了后台应用能即时运行。但有部分第三方应用放在后台后，会不断连接网络或者不断运行引起耗电。一般来讲，耗电越快，手机发热越明显。当您感觉到手机明显发热时，请查看耗电是否正常（可通过设置-省电管理-耗电详情-后台耗电应用，查看后台耗电应用），如果有耗电大且不是您正在用的软件，请将其关闭。夏季尽量不要长时间在阳光下使用手机，或将手机放在车前部阳光照射下导航，可以避免手机因太阳照射而发热。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8265","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748652000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":98,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"发热","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}